attributes.description:
2016 BMW 120D AUTO FACE LIFT, 149 800 000 KM’S, FULL SERVICE HISTORY MOSTLY BY BMW  R 259 950.00, GREAT FUEL SAVER
 If you are looking for great economy, comfort, power all in one car I would have to say this is the one you should look at. It’s amazing to me how this BME diesel engine performs, Please don’t think because it’s a diesel it’s slow. These 1 series diesel motors move nicely when you want them to, and the best thing about this car is that no matter how hard or soft you drive it its always sitting under 7ltrs per 100 Km’s. 
This is also the face lift version, it was only released in 2016. You simply cannot compare the looks of the facelift to the previous generation. Some people might say this is high mileage for a 2016, but it’s not, these cars sell for a high price, if this car had 80 000 Km’s I would be selling it for well over R300K. Also this motor is seriously one of the most reliable engines to come out of the BMW stable, so much more reliable than its petrol derivative. 
Me personally I feel that the only thing this car is missing is a nice set of tinted windows, then it will look perfect in my eyes. So if the new owner decides they want tinted windows, we will fit them on us, that’s it FREE SMASH AND GRAB ON US. And we only use the best Auto Armor. 
WHAT MAKES THIS CAR SPECIAL
•	Brand New 18 inch M-Sport Wheels
•	Face lift version
•	Sunroof
•	Under 5 LTRS Per 100 Km’s on the open road 
•	Full BMW factory leather interior
•	Bluetooth
•	Park distance control
